COMMITTEE AMENDMENT

COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to H.P. 18, L.D. 54
1 Amend the bill by relettering or renumbering any nonconsecutive Part letter or section
2 number to read consecutively.
3 SUMMARY
44 This amendment, which is the majority report of the committee, amends the bill to
55 exempt compensation based solely on commission from the definition of "range of pay"
66 and authorizes employers to satisfy the required range of pay posting for positions
77 compensated based solely on commission by providing a statement to applicants that the
88 position is compensated based solely on commission.
